<refentry version="5.0-subset Scilab" xml:id="ipcv_version" xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
<refnamediv><refname>ipcv_version</refname><refpurpose>Return IPCV and runtime dependency version information.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>info = ipcv_version()</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>ipcv_version</function> returns a structure containing the IPCV package version, the OpenCV version used by the loaded native gateway, the Scilab version, platform, and architecture.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting><![CDATA[
info = ipcv_version();
disp(info.ipcv);
disp(info.opencv);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
